Interface Carpart

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Airco, Body, Color, Engine, Gearbox, Seats, Spoiler, Wheels

    public interface Carpart
    interface for representing all carParts a carpart knows how to install itself and whether or not it has been installed already on a given car.
